slidezilla
==========

Unix script to create a video by using many images and video clips.

The goal is to be able to perform all the operations that are currently supported by 
iMovie or MovieMaker using this unix script. 

You can provide a config file with input details as a parameters to the script.


Features
========

1) Use Images and/or videos as input for the final video
2) Specify the background music file. 
3) You can also use the in-built effects or add more custom effects. 
4) You can also add titles for each image or video


Usage 
=====

slidezilla.sh  <-debug> -cf /path/to/config_file


